Dear [Recipient Name],

Subject: Service Certificate for Mr. A.K.H.A.R. Wijesingha

This letter serves as a formal Service Certificate for Mr. A.K.H.A.R. Wijesingha, an Authorized Officer at the Department of Immigration and Emigration.

Mr. A.K.H.A.R. Wijesingha has been an integral part of our team, serving diligently and effectively in various capacities. He commenced his tenure as an Enforcement Officer on 15.07.2005 and transitioned to the role of Authorized Officer on 15.09.2011. Throughout his service, Mr. Wijesingha has demonstrated commendable dedication, professionalism, and commitment to his responsibilities.

It is hereby confirmed that Mr. A.K.H.A.R. Wijesingha's position as an Authorized Officer is permanent and pensionable within our department. His anticipated retirement date is set for 26.02.2033.

This Service Certificate is issued at the specific request of Mr. A.K.H.A.R. Wijesingha for his personal records.

Should you require any further verification or information regarding Mr. Wijesingha's service, please do not hesitate to contact us.

Yours sincerely,

[Your Name]
[Your Position]

